OL,7,FITV News Meridian's Kit Bradshaw
OL,8,Freports from Portsmouth on devolution
OL,9,Fto Hampshire and the Solent
OL,11,FHampshire and the Isle of Wight's
OL,12,Fpolice and crime commissioner has
OL,13,Fannounced she intends to stand to
OL,14,Fbecome one of the region's first
OL,15,Fdirectly-elected mayors.
OL,17,FDonna Jones hopes to be selected as
OL,18,Fthe Conservative candidate for the new
OL,19,Fposition of Mayor of Hampshire and the
OL,20,FSolent, with the first election
OL,21,Fplanned for May 2026.
