OL,5,Cmayor position
OL,7,FThe government is currently running a
OL,8,Fpublic consultation on its plans for a
OL,9,Fmayor and a combined strategic
OL,10,Fauthority for the area, which would
OL,11,Fcover Hampshire, Portsmouth,
OL,12,FSouthampton and the Isle of Wight.
OL,14,FMs Jones told ITV News: "This role is
OL,15,Fabout bringing overseas investment
OL,16,Finto Hampshire and the Isle of Wight,
OL,17,Fattracting more jobs, more opportunity
OL,18,Fto our area, growing the prosperity,
OL,19,Fmaking sure more houses get built, and
OL,20,Fdelivering really high quality public
OL,21,Fservices."
