OL,7,FDonna Jones' current role of PCC would
OL,8,Fbe abolished, under the devolution
OL,9,Fplans, with the mayor assuming
OL,10,Foversight of policing and fire
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,FThe new elected politician would also
OL,14,Fget powers over transport, strategic
OL,15,Fplanning, skills, health and
OL,16,Fregeneration.
