OL,7,FLabour MP Satvir Kaur, who represents
OL,8,FSouthampton Test, said: "Places like
OL,9,FSouthampton have so much potential and
OL,10,Feveryone talks about realising that
OL,11,Fpotential. I really believe that
OL,12,Fdevolution can unlock that."
OL,14,FReform UK and the Liberal Democrats
OL,15,Fhave raised concerns about the linked
OL,16,Freorganisation of local councils in
OL,17,Fthe area, which has delayed some
OL,18,Felections by at least a year.
